    <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">Introduction</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" class="mt-5 mb-5">
        As part of the course project at HKUST of ELEC3300 Introduction to Embedded System, I have developed a water-proofed amphibious drone with tilting rotors that can fly in the air, move on the road, and sail on water. 
        In this project, I designed, built, and tested the drone's custom mechanical structure, microcontroller circuit, and flight control algorithm.
        Here's the render of the final design.
    </MudText>
